{"code":200,"status":"OK","data":{"number":83,"name":"\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0645\u064f\u0637\u064e\u0641\u0651\u0650\u0641\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e","englishName":"Al-Mutaffifin","englishNameTranslation":"Defrauding","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":36,"ayahs":[{"number":5849,"text":"Malheur aux fraudeurs","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5850,"text":"qui, lorsqu'ils font mesurer pour eux-m\u00eames exigent la pleine mesure,","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5851,"text":"et qui lorsqu'eux-m\u00eames mesurent ou p\u00e8sent pour les autres, [leur] causent perte.","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5852,"text":"Ceux-l\u00e0 ne pensent-ils pas qu'ils seront ressuscit\u00e9s,","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5853,"text":"en un jour terrible,","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5854,"text":"le jour o\u00f9 les gens se tiendront debout devant le Seigneur de l'Univers?","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":587,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5855,"text":"Non...! Mais en v\u00e9rit\u00e9 le livre des libertins sera dans le Sijj\u00een -","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5856,"text":"et qui te dira ce qu'est le Sijj\u00een? -","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5857,"text":"Un livre d\u00e9j\u00e0 cachet\u00e9 (achev\u00e9).","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5858,"text":"Malheur, ce jour-l\u00e0, aux n\u00e9gateurs,","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5859,"text":"qui d\u00e9mentent le jour de la R\u00e9tribution.","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5860,"text":"Or, ne le d\u00e9ment que tout transgresseur, p\u00e9cheur:","numberInSurah":12,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5861,"text":"qui, lorsque Nos versets lui sont r\u00e9cit\u00e9s, dit: \u00ab[Ce sont] des contes d'anciens!\u00bb","numberInSurah":13,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5862,"text":"Pas du tout, mais ce qu'ils ont accompli couvre leurs c\u0153urs.","numberInSurah":14,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5863,"text":"Qu'ils prennent garde! En v\u00e9rit\u00e9 ce jour-l\u00e0 un voile les emp\u00eachera de voir leur Seigneur,","numberInSurah":15,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5864,"text":"ensuite, ils br\u00fbleront certes, dans la Fournaise;","numberInSurah":16,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5865,"text":"on [leur] dira alors: \u00abVoil\u00e0 ce que vous traitiez de mensonge!\u00bb","numberInSurah":17,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5866,"text":"Qu'ils prennent garde! Le livre des bons sera dans l'Illiy\u00fbn -","numberInSurah":18,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5867,"text":"et qui te dira ce qu'est l'Illiy\u00fbn? -","numberInSurah":19,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5868,"text":"un livre cachet\u00e9!","numberInSurah":20,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5869,"text":"Les rapproch\u00e9s [d'Allah: les Anges] en t\u00e9moignent.","numberInSurah":21,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5870,"text":"Les bons seront dans [un Jardin] de d\u00e9lice,","numberInSurah":22,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5871,"text":"sur les divans, ils regardent.","numberInSurah":23,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5872,"text":"Tu reconna\u00eetras sur leurs visages, l'\u00e9clat de la f\u00e9licit\u00e9.","numberInSurah":24,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5873,"text":"On leur sert \u00e0 boire un nectar pur, cachet\u00e9,","numberInSurah":25,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5874,"text":"laissant un arri\u00e8re-go\u00fbt de musc. Que ceux qui la convoitent entrent en comp\u00e9tition [pour l'acqu\u00e9rir]","numberInSurah":26,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5875,"text":"Il est m\u00e9lang\u00e9 \u00e0 la boisson de Tasn\u00eem,","numberInSurah":27,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5876,"text":"source dont les rapproch\u00e9s boivent.","numberInSurah":28,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5877,"text":"Les criminels riaient de ceux qui croyaient,","numberInSurah":29,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5878,"text":"et, passant pr\u00e8s d'eux, ils se faisaient des \u0153illades,","numberInSurah":30,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5879,"text":"et, retournant dans leurs familles, ils retournaient en plaisantant,","numberInSurah":31,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5880,"text":"et les voyant, ils disaient: \u00abCe sont vraiment ceux-l\u00e0 les \u00e9gar\u00e9s\u00bb.","numberInSurah":32,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5881,"text":"Or, ils n'ont pas \u00e9t\u00e9 envoy\u00e9s pour \u00eatre leurs gardiens.","numberInSurah":33,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5882,"text":"Aujourd'hui, donc, ce sont ceux qui ont cru qui rient des infid\u00e8les","numberInSurah":34,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":588,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5883,"text":"sur les divans, ils regardent.","numberInSurah":35,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":589,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false},{"number":5884,"text":"Est-ce que les infid\u00e8les ont eu la r\u00e9compense de ce qu'ils faisaient?","numberInSurah":36,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":589,"ruku":525,"hizbQuarter":235,"sajda":false}],"edition":{"identifier":"fr.hamidullah","language":"fr","name":"Hamidullah","englishName":"Muhammad Hamidullah","format":"text","type":"translation","direction":"ltr"}}}